      • dispatch

        void dispatch(ServletRequest request,
              ServletResponse response)
       throws ServletException,
              IOException
        Perform an asynchronous dispatch. The method does not check if the request is in an appropriate state for this; it is the caller's responsibility to check this.
        参数:
        request - The request object to pass to the dispatch target
        response - The response object to pass to the dispatch target
        抛出:
        ServletException - if thrown by the dispatch target
        IOException - if an I/O error occurs while processing the dispatch
